00:00:04,426 --> 00:00:07,546
Hamster Hide-and-Seek
小仓鼠  藏猫猫

2
00:00:09,128 --> 00:00:13,120
Over my arm she softly flows
她轻柔地掠过我的手臂

3
00:00:13,822 --> 00:00:18,320
cinnamon coat and whiskery nose.
肉桂色的皮毛和长满胡须的鼻翼

4
00:00:18,871 --> 00:00:23,848
With marble eyes she stops and peeks,
停下来圆溜溜的大眼睛四处查看

5
00:00:24,408 --> 00:00:28,684
lets me stroke her knapsack cheeks.
我不禁抚摸她那布袋般的脸蛋

6
00:00:30,017 --> 00:00:34,008
Then ripple-of-fur takes her leave
只那么一触 她身子一拱 

7
00:00:34,062 --> 00:00:39,280
to probe new roads inside my sleeve.
前去探索 我的袖笼

